thread.title: Stephen Lane
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Stephen Lane

author: Stephen Lane
title: Stephen Lane
text: I booked the premium booking. It was booked to be picked up by their partner DHL on a specific date between specific times. I made sure I was home all day for it. Nobody turned up. I got an email and it said to call the Townsville office if I had any questions. They knew nothing about it and made me feel very uncomfortable about the entire situation. I then had to actually drop the box in myself and was not even given any tracking details. This was possibly the worst parcel sending experience I have had outside Aust Post.
